go into the sea first!" As they stood there bickering, Nah/±shon ben
Aminadav jumped into the water. Meanwhile Moses was praying. God said
to him, "My friend is drowning--and you pray!" "What can I do?" Moses
asked. [God responded as it says in the text,] "Speak to the people of Israel
and tell them to go! Raise your staff..."    /SC/XXTALMUD SOTAH 37A/XX/PR

